channel.description:
Well i was editing some things on my server. After words i decided to post it up. but i had to redo the *how to make a server guide* because the server status page said i was offline. then when i tried to run the server it would pop out then back out super fast. Then i tryed to open my silbv5 client and it got an error saying
` java` is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file. press any key to continue . . .
and so i think that was the same error it got when i tried to run the server. main question is.. How do i get my server running again? Any help would be greatly appreciated=D Thanks again.
